title: Sidewall, ca. 1875
provenance: Found in the nave of St. John's Church, Cookstown, Ontario. paper has been rubbed and is mottled. Mounted on muslin.
description: Fragment of irregular outline. All-over pattern of vine foliage set with conventionalized floral shapes, in slight outline.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, ca. 1875.
ca. 1875. Machine-printed. Gift of Kenneth E. Kidd. 1947-109-1.
